A Ralts has the power to sense the emotions of people and Pok√©mon with the horns on its head. It takes cover if it senses any hostility.
A Kirlia has the psychic power to create a rip in the dimensions and see into the future. It is said to dance with pleasure on sunny mornings.
It apparently does not feel the pull of gravity because it supports itself with psychic power. It will give its life to protect its Trainer.
A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows when trying to protect someone. It can sense what its foe is thinking.
